perturbations.original:
\[
r = r(q,t) =
\begin{cases}
q - 1, & t = 1, \\[1mm]
2q - 3, & t = 2 \text{~~~or~~~}t=q=3, \\[1mm]
\displaystyle (q - t + 1)t, & 3 \le t < \frac{q+1}{2}, \\[1mm]
\displaystyle \left\lfloor (q + 1)^2/4 \right\rfloor, & \text{otherwise.}
\end{cases}
\]

